graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator (DSPO)"
        Controller[DSPO Controller<br/>Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Admission Controller]
        Controller -->|manages| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "DSPA Instance Components"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent<br/>Background Service]
        ScheduledWF[Scheduled Workflow Controller<br/>Background Service]
        WorkflowController[Workflow Controller<br/>Argo Controller]
        MLPipelinesUI[ML Pipelines UI<br/>Web Frontend - Optional]
        MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy<br/>Proxy - Optional]
        MLMDgRPC[MLMD gRPC<br/>Service - Optional]

        APIServer -->|uses| WorkflowController
        PersistenceAgent -->|syncs status| WorkflowController
        ScheduledWF -->|creates| WorkflowController
        MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMDgRPC
    end

    subgraph "Storage Components (Optional)"
        MariaDB[MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP]
        Minio[Minio<br/>9000/TCP S3]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        DSPA[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
        Pipeline[Pipeline CR]
        PipelineVersion[PipelineVersion CR]
        Workflow[Workflow CR]
        ScheduledWorkflow[ScheduledWorkflow CR]
    end

    %% Operator interactions
    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPA
    DSPA -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|deploys| APIServer
    Controller -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|deploys| ScheduledWF
    Controller -->|deploys| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|deploys| MariaDB
    Controller -->|deploys| Minio

    Webhook -->|validates/mutates| PipelineVersion

    %% CRD interactions
    APIServer -->|creates| Pipeline
    APIServer -->|creates| PipelineVersion
    APIServer -->|creates| Workflow
    ScheduledWF -->|creates| ScheduledWorkflow

    %% Data persistence
    APIServer -->|stores metadata| MariaDB
    PersistenceAgent -->|stores status| MariaDB
    MLMDgRPC -->|stores lineage| MariaDB
    APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
    WorkflowController -->|stores artifacts| Minio

    %% External dependencies
    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    Controller -->|depends on| ArgoWorkflows[Argo Workflows 3.5.14]
    APIServer -->|integrates| KServe[KServe]
    APIServer -->|integrates| Ray[Ray]
    APIServer -->|integrates| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External storage
    APIServer -.->|or external| ExternalS3[External S3]
    APIServer -.->|or external| ExternalDB[External MySQL/MariaDB]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style APIServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DSPA fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style MariaDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Minio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ArgoWorkflows fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ExternalS3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ExternalDB fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
